# 🌤 Pro Weather App (No API Key)

A lightweight, professional weather app built with **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.  
It uses **OpenStreetMap (Nominatim)** for geocoding and **Open-Meteo** for weather data — both are free and require **no API key**.

---

## 🚀 Features
- Search weather by **city / country name**
- **Geolocation** support (📍 button finds your current location)
- Toggle between **°C and °F**
- Clean & modern responsive UI (desktop + mobile)
- Weather condition **icons & text descriptions**
- Shows **wind speed, pressure, humidity** (extendable)
- Accessible (ARIA roles, keyboard-friendly)
- Powered by **open APIs** — no signup needed

